summary.title: Online Banking Application Threat Model
summary.description: Online banking applications are prime targets for cyber threats due to their handling of sensitive financial data. Threat model for a new online banking application, focusing on identifying potential security threats and proposing mitigation strategies using the STRIDE methodology.
